&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Required:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious, problem solving, and open-minded approach to work; we are looking for someone who has a base of knowledge but wants to investigate and learn new things&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience or training working with large data sets to identify trends, answer questions, and diagnose inconsistencies&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
